                        </a></div></div><ol class="sense_single" htag="ol"><li class="sense" hclass="sense" id="americanbreakfast_sng_1" htag="li"><span class="sensetop" htag="span" hclass="sensetop"><span class="def" hclass="def" htag="span">a large breakfast that can include <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/cereal" title="cereal definition"><span class="ndv">cereal</span></a> and cooked food, such as eggs with <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/ham_1" title="ham definition"><span class="ndv">ham</span></a></span></span><div class="collapse" htag="div" hclass="collapse"><span class="unbox" unbox="cult" id="americanbreakfast_unbox_1" source="ald9_guide"><span class="box_title">Culture</span><span class="body"><span class="p">An American breakfast usually includes several choices from such items as juice, <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/cereal" title="cereal definition"><span class="ndv">cereal</span></a>, eggs with <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/ham_1" title="ham definition"><span class="ndv">ham</span></a> or <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/bacon" title="bacon definition"><span class="ndv">bacon</span></a>, <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/pancake" title="pancakes definition"><span class="ndv">pancakes</span></a>, <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/toast_1" title="toast definition"><span class="ndv">toast</span></a> , and <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/hash-browns" title="hash browns definition"><span class="ndv">hash browns</span></a> or, in the southern states, <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/grits" title="grits defini